data.description: Welcome to the scenic Makaha Valley Plantations, where this 2-bedroom unit awaits in a secure gated community. Embrace a lifestyle of comfort and recreation surrounded by mature tropical grounds. Experience the peace of mind that comes with 24-hour security, a serene living environment. Delight in the resort-style amenities, including two pools, Jacuzzis, tennis and basketball courts, and barbecue areas for entertaining friends and family. This unit offers upgrades to the kitchen cabinets, countertops, bathroom tub and toilet. With a convenient location near the entry, arriving and departing is hassle-free. Plus, you’re just minutes from the stunning Makaha Beach! Schedule a tour today!
